Dialogue: 10,0:00:14.36,0:00:16.21,GJM_Main,Ohta,0,0,0,,Is this what you wanted, Miyano?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:16.21,0:00:18.50,GJM_Main,M,0,0,0,,Thank you very much, Ohta-kun!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:18.50,0:00:20.40,GJM_Main,Tanaka,0,0,0,,Good for you, Miyano-san.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:20.40,0:00:22.00,GJM_Main,M,0,0,0,,Yes, Master!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:27.16,0:00:29.96,GJM_Main,M,0,0,0,,There's really nothing better than strawberry milk!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:30.46,0:00:37.17,GJM_Main,M,0,0,0,,Still, I can't believe they changed the position.\NI can't reach the button anymore.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:37.17,0:00:39.81,GJM_Main,M,0,0,0,,It's not easy being small.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:40.21,0:00:41.78,GJM_Main,Tanaka,0,0,0,,Sounds tough.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:41.78,0:00:43.30,GJM_Main,M,0,0,0,,It really is.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:43.30,0:00:45.62,GJM_Main,M,0,0,0,,I run into a lot of problems because I'm small!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:45.62,0:00:48.31,GJM_Main,M,0,0,0,,I'm jealous of you, Ohta-kun! You're so tall.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:48.53,0:00:50.17,GJM_Main,Ohta,0,0,0,,Being tall isn't good either.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:50.17,0:00:53.82,GJM_Main,Ohta,0,0,0,,It can be pretty inconvenient sometimes.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:53.82,0:00:56.20,GJM_Main,Ohta,0,0,0,,I hit my head a lot, for example.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:56.59,0:01:00.84,GJM_Main,M,0,0,0,,When you're small, there aren't any cool,\Nmature-looking clothes and shoes,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:00.84,0:01:03.20,GJM_Main,M,0,0,0,,and even if you try wearing them,\Nthey don't suit you!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:03.58,0:01:06.83,GJM_Main,Ohta,0,0,0,,When you're big,\Nthere aren't many clothes to choose from.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:06.83,0:01:07.74,GJM_Main,M,0,0,0,,But, but!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:07.74,0:01:12.84,GJM_Main,M,0,0,0,,When I want to buy a ticket for a bus,\Nthey ask me if I want a children's one!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:12.84,0:01:15.97,GJM_Main,Ohta,0,0,0,,When I want to buy a student ticket in a cinema,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:15.97,0:01:19.35,GJM_Main,Ohta,0,0,0,,they ask me if I'm really in high school,\Neven when I show them my student ID.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:19.82,0:01:23.00,GJM_Main,Tanaka,0,0,0,,Now now, you two, no need to get so heated.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:23.00,0:01:27.83,GJM_Main,M,0,0,0,,My stomach is too small\Nto eat all of the things I like!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:27.83,0:01:31.27,GJM_Main,Ohta,0,0,0,,When I wait in line in a confectionery,\Npeople give me weird looks.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:31.27,0:01:33.43,GJM_Main,M,0,0,0,,I can't reach the luggage rack on a train!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:33.43,0:01:37.56,GJM_Main,Ohta,0,0,0,,When I go to a cinema, I'm worried people\Nbehind me can't see because of me!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:37.56,0:01:40.88,GJM_Main,M,0,0,0,,In toilets, hangers are usually\Nso high I can't reach them!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:55.26,0:01:56.87,GJM_Main,M,0,0,0,,When I'm walking,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:56.87,0:02:00.26,GJM_Main,M,0,0,0,,sometimes I get candies from grandmas\NI don't know telling me I'm cute!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:00.26,0:02:04.25,GJM_Main,Ohta,0,0,0,,When I get close to a girl\Nto save her from shady people,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:04.25,0:02:07.52,GJM_Main,Ohta,0,0,0,,they run away the second\Nthey see me and she thanks me.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:07.52,0:02:11.16,GJM_Main,M,0,0,0,,I'm close to the ground,\Nso I notice dropped things a lot!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:11.16,0:02:13.90,GJM_Main,Ohta,0,0,0,,I can reach high places, so it's convenient!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:26.14,0:02:28.46,GJM_Main,M,0,0,0,,I'm jealous of tall people.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:28.90,0:02:31.46,GJM_Main,Ohta,0,0,0,,Being small isn't bad either.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:32.00,0:02:35.62,GJM_Main,Tanaka,0,0,0,,In the end, everyone just wants\Nwhat they don't have.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:36.22,0:02:38.34,GJM_Main,Tanaka,0,0,0,,I'm so glad I'm ordinary.
